
<p align="center">Road Map</p>
===

Todos
---
* call functions to return html
* render custom attrs when tag is closed, not when open
* handle changes to a prop
* handle changes to custom attributes
* define your own custom attributes
* add features form old quas version:
  * scroll locking
  * scroll tacker/breakpoints
  * browser info
  * url values
* fix ajax request to work with $_POST and $_GET
* states, start -> loading -> finished rendering -> ready (this must be optional)
* Cookies
 * cookie(key,val,date,directory) - get/set cookie, clear cookie by passing empty string
* Playground
* Documentation
  * Quas.formChildren([json,json,[json,json], josn) - return 1D array of josn objects
  * Comments
  * Read.me
  * Landing page

---

Component Package
----
A number of components which will accelerate prototyping (look at bootstrap too)
* Type of components:
 * Modal
 * Body
 * Navbar
 * Footer
 * Sidebar
 * Comments
 * Cards


* CSS Notes:
 * Flexbox rather than inline-blocks
 * Reuseable CSS classes
